OL,3,CWhat's the difference between whooping
OL,4,Ccough and a normal cough?
OL,6,FThe UK is experiencing a rapid rise in
OL,7,F, with almost 5,000 cases confirmed
OL,8,Fbetween January and April 2024 and
OL,9,Feight infant deaths.
OL,11,FNew figures from the UK Health
OL,12,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA) show 1,888
OL,13,Fcases of the illness were detected in
OL,14,FApril, up from 1,319 cases in March,
OL,15,F918 in February and 556 in January.
OL,16,FThis compares to just 858 cases of
OL,17,Fwhooping cough for the whole of 2023.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/16
