OL,3,CWhat's the difference between whooping
OL,4,Ccough and a normal cough?
OL,6,FThe jump in cases between March and
OL,7,FApril 2024 is the biggest increase so
OL,8,Ffar this year - with 569 more cases
OL,9,Freported.
OL,11,FEight infants are also known to have
OL,12,Fdied in between January and April
OL,13,F2024. Three of those died in April
OL,14,Falone.
OL,16,FSpeaking before the data for April was
OL,17,Freleased, Dr Michael Head, Senior
OL,18,FResearch Fellow in Global Health told
OL,19,FITV News these figures are significant
OL,20,F- but not unprecedented.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/16
