OL,3,CWhat's the difference between whooping
OL,4,Ccough and a normal cough?
OL,6,F"The data is definitely concerning,"
OL,7,Fhe said.
OL,9,F"We do see large outbreaks of whooping
OL,10,Fcough on a cycle every few years but
OL,11,Fthe one we're seeing at the moment is
OL,12,Fbig."
OL,14,FBut what has caused this most recent
OL,15,Fspike in cases, and how simple is it
OL,16,Fto tell the difference between
OL,17,Fwhooping cough and a regular cough?
OL,19,FWhat is whooping cough?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/16
