OL,3,CWhat's the difference between whooping
OL,4,Ccough and a normal cough?
OL,6,FThose with the illness may make a
OL,7,F'whoop' sound, caused by gasping for
OL,8,Fbreath between coughs - but this does
OL,9,Fnot happen everyone with whooping
OL,10,Fcough.
OL,12,FIt can cause breathing difficulties,
OL,13,Fwith young infants turning blue or
OL,14,Fgrey and adults becoming red in the
OL,15,Fface after coughing bouts.
OL,17,FWhooping cough may also bring up thick
OL,18,Fmucus, which can cause vomiting.
OL,20,FHow is it different to a normal cough?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/16
