OL,3,CWhat's the difference between whooping
OL,4,Ccough and a normal cough?
OL,6,FDr Head explained whooping cough is
OL,7,Fsimilar to other kinds of respiratory
OL,8,Fillness in the early stages.
OL,10,FHe said: "You'll have some kind of
OL,11,Fcough, and perhaps a runny nose or a
OL,12,Ffever. It is very, very hard to tell
OL,13,Fthe difference at that stage between
OL,14,Fwhooping cough and anything else.
OL,16,F"You can only really notice it's
OL,17,Fwhooping cough later on in the
OL,18,Fpresentation when that distinctive
OL,19,F'hoop' sound kicks in."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/16
