OL,3,CWhat's the difference between whooping
OL,4,Ccough and a normal cough?
OL,6,FGiven not everyone experiences this
OL,7,Fsymptom, the illness is difficult to
OL,8,Faccurately diagnose without laboratory
OL,9,Ftesting, according to Dr Head.
OL,11,F"That's another reason why it is hard
OL,12,Fto get outbreaks under control and why
OL,13,Fvaccination is vital," he said.
OL,15,FHow serious is it?
OL,17,FWhooping cough can lead to serious and
OL,18,Fsometimes deadly complications in
OL,19,Fbabies and young children.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/16
