OL,3,CWhat's the difference between whooping
OL,4,Ccough and a normal cough?
OL,6,FAround a third of babies under the age
OL,7,Fof one with whooping cough will need
OL,8,Fhospital care.
OL,10,FComplications can include apnea (life-
OL,11,Fthreatening pauses in breathing),
OL,12,Fpneumonia, convulsions and
OL,13,Fencephalopathy (disease of the brain).
OL,15,FTeenagers and adults can also
OL,16,Fexperience complications, but they are
OL,17,Fgenerally less serious in those who
OL,18,Fare older.
OL,20,FWhat has caused this recent outbreak?
