OL,3,CWhat's the difference between whooping
OL,4,Ccough and a normal cough?
OL,6,FAccording to Dr Head, outbreaks of
OL,7,Fwhooping cough happen every few years.
OL,9,FHe said: "The reasons are not totally
OL,10,Fclear but will be related to drops in
OL,11,Fvaccine uptake and probably waning of
OL,12,Fimmunity in older children and younger
OL,13,Fadults.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/16
