OL,3,CWhat's the difference between whooping
OL,4,Ccough and a normal cough?
OL,6,F"Once you get to that sort of nine or
OL,7,Ften years of age, the immunity from
OL,8,Fthe vaccines does start to wear off.
OL,9,FWaning of immunity and any lower
OL,10,Fvaccine uptake does mean the
OL,11,Fvulnerable populations like children
OL,12,Fand pregnant women are more likely to
OL,13,Fbe exposed."
OL,15,FDr Head believes the time of year
OL,16,Fcould explain the uptick in cases
OL,17,Facross the past few months.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/16
